item.title: Football: Men’s 7s make light work of Heythrop
item.author: Edward Lambourn,
item.description: Football Men’s 3rd – 2 Sussex 2nd – 1 A fine afternoon in Fulham yielded a impressive 4-0 away victory for the Imperial football 7th team against a strong Heythrop side whose Kensington location made it as close to a derby game as any possible outside Varsity week.
